Stage D - Python Container
===========================

Docker Image Details
--------------------
Image: fasta-analysis:latest
Base Image: python:3.11-slim
Size: 368 MB

Dependencies Installed
- matplotlib: For histogram visualization
- pandas: For data processing (optional but included)

Build Command
-------------
docker build -t fasta-analysis:latest .

Run Commands
------------

1. Default execution (ATG motif):
   docker run --rm -v $(pwd)/results:/app/results fasta-analysis:latest

2. Custom motif analysis (GC):
   docker run --rm -v $(pwd)/results:/app/results fasta-analysis:latest \
     python3 fasta_analysis.py data/sequences/sample_sequences.fasta GC results

3. Interactive mode:
   docker run --rm -it -v $(pwd)/results:/app/results fasta-analysis:latest /bin/bash

Container Environment
---------------------
Working Directory: /app
Data Location: /app/data/sequences
Output Location: /app/results
Python Version: 3.11

Volume Mapping
--------------
-v /workspaces/BashForDummies/results:/app/results
  Maps local results directory to container for output persistence

