8. Container runs with --rm flag (auto-cleanup)

Dockerfile Features
-------------------
- Minimal Python base image (3.11-slim)
- No cache for pip install (smaller final image)
- PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 for immediate output
- Pre-created output directories
- Default command configured for ATG analysis
- Compatible with custom command overrides
